<div class="post-headline">		<h2>			
			<a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2008/03/14/intern-wanted/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Intern Wanted">Intern Wanted</a></h2>
		</div>

<div class="post-bodycopy clearfix"><p>Do you like filling in forms? Do you like putting things in envelopes? Do you like going to the post office? How about running errands? All for no money!</p>
<p>If this sounds like your dream job, I need someone to come to my unglamorous Manhattan studio once a week and do all of the above. You can probably get college credit for it. And learn something? Apply here.</p>
<p>
above: just some of the mess you could help clean up!</p>
